datasets.name: 6cee62b2
queryLines:
SELECT designator, home_location, lat, long,
    CASE 
        WHEN MAX(CASE WHEN operable = 'false' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) >= 1 THEN 'red'
        WHEN COUNT(fault) >= 1 THEN 'yellow'
        ELSE 'green'
    END AS status 
FROM ship_current_status_gold
GROUP BY ALL;

datasets.name: 4bf52947
queryLines:
SELECT COUNT(*) num_faults, p.type FROM ship_current_status_gold AS s
LEFT JOIN parts p
ON find_in_set(s.prediction, array_join(p.sensors, ',')) > 0
WHERE prediction != 'ok' AND type IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY ALL

datasets.name: 66f9103e
queryLines:
WITH s AS (
    SELECT prediction, home_location, COUNT(*) num_faults
    FROM ship_current_status_gold
    GROUP BY prediction, home_location
), 
p AS (
    SELECT stock_location, parts.type part, stock_available stock, 
            CASE 
                WHEN stock_location = 'FLC Norfolk' THEN 'NB Norfolk'
                WHEN stock_location = 'FLC Jacksonville' THEN 'NS Mayport'
                WHEN stock_location = 'FLC San Diego' THEN 'NB San Diego'
                WHEN stock_location = 'FLC Pearl Harbor' THEN 'NS Pearl Harbor'
                WHEN stock_location = 'FLC Puget Sound' THEN 'NB San Diego'
            END nearest_homeport
            , sensor  -- Include a new column to store the exploded sensor value
    FROM parts
    LATERAL VIEW explode(sensors) p_ex AS sensor
)

SELECT p.stock_location, p.part, p.stock, s.home_location, (s.num_faults - p.stock) AS deficit
FROM s
LEFT JOIN p ON s.prediction = p.sensor AND p.nearest_homeport = s.home_location
WHERE (s.num_faults - p.stock) > 0 AND (s.num_faults - p.stock) IS NOT NULL;

CAST(lat AS DOUBLE) AS lat,

datasets.name: f0a18247
queryLines:
WITH srn AS (
  SELECT 
    REPLACE(designator, '_', ' ') AS designator, 
    type, 
    stock_location, 
    qty_shipped 
  FROM 
    shipment_recommendations
)
SELECT 
  srn.*, 
  sm.home_location 
FROM 
  srn
JOIN 
  ship_meta AS sm 
ON 
  sm.designator LIKE CONCAT('%', srn.designator, '%')
WHERE srn.qty_shipped > 0

datasets.name: 8a940a4b
queryLines:
WITH homes AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT designator, home_location 
  FROM ship_meta
)
SELECT qty_shipped, type, stock_location, shipment_recommendations.designator, homes.home_location 
FROM shipment_recommendations
JOIN homes ON shipment_recommendations.designator = homes.designator
WHERE qty_shipped > 0
